{"item_id":"df94771dc6:0","text":"Materials（材质）控制对象的外观，而 patterns（图案节点）通过在曲面上改变材质 Bxdf 的 parameters（参数）来控制细节。这类似于 texture artists（纹理艺术家）使用 textures（纹理）控制材质外观的方式。RenderMan 随附一组 patterns，可用于 texturing（纹理处理）、color correction（颜色校正）、bumping（凹凸）以及各种 utility shading systems（实用着色系统）。"}
{"item_id":"df94771dc6:1","text":"这些 patterns（图案节点）可分为以下类别："}
{"item_id":"df94771dc6:2","text":"Image Texture（图像纹理）"}
{"item_id":"df94771dc6:3","text":"使用 texture images（纹理图像）驱动 patterns（图案节点）。"}
{"item_id":"df94771dc6:4","text":"PxrMultiTexture"}
{"item_id":"df94771dc6:5","text":"PxrProjectionLayer"}
{"item_id":"df94771dc6:6","text":"PxrPtexture"}
{"item_id":"df94771dc6:7","text":"PxrTexture"}
{"item_id":"df94771dc6:8","text":"Procedural Texture（程序化纹理）"}
{"item_id":"df94771dc6:9","text":"以 procedural（程序化）方式创建 noise（噪声）和 patterns（图案）。"}
{"item_id":"df94771dc6:10","text":"PxrChecker"}
{"item_id":"df94771dc6:11","text":"PxrCurvature"}
{"item_id":"df94771dc6:12","text":"PxrFractal"}
{"item_id":"df94771dc6:13","text":"PxrVoronoise"}
{"item_id":"df94771dc6:14","text":"PxrWorley"}
{"item_id":"df94771dc6:15","text":"PxrPhasorNoise"}
{"item_id":"df94771dc6:16","text":"Manifolds（流形）"}
{"item_id":"df94771dc6:17","text":"Manifolds（流形）会告诉渲染器如何在曲面上应用 patterns（图案节点）。这会控制 repetition（重复）、placement（放置）和 size（大小）等特性。"}
{"item_id":"df94771dc6:18","text":"PxrManifold2D"}
{"item_id":"df94771dc6:19","text":"PxrBumpManifold2D"}
{"item_id":"df94771dc6:20","text":"PxrManifold3D"}
{"item_id":"df94771dc6:21","text":"PxrProjector"}
{"item_id":"df94771dc6:22","text":"PxrRandomTextureManifold"}
{"item_id":"df94771dc6:23","text":"PxrRoundCube"}
{"item_id":"df94771dc6:24","text":"PxrTileManifold"}
{"item_id":"df94771dc6:25","text":"PxrHexTileManifold"}
{"item_id":"df94771dc6:26","text":"Color（颜色）"}
{"item_id":"df94771dc6:27","text":"在 shading network（着色网络）中创建或修改颜色。"}
{"item_id":"df94771dc6:28","text":"PxrBlackBody"}
{"item_id":"df94771dc6:29","text":"PxrBlend"}
{"item_id":"df94771dc6:30","text":"PxrClamp"}
{"item_id":"df94771dc6:31","text":"PxrColorCorrect"}
{"item_id":"df94771dc6:32","text":"PxrColorSpace"}
{"item_id":"df94771dc6:33","text":"PxrExposure"}
{"item_id":"df94771dc6:34","text":"PxrGamma"}
{"item_id":"df94771dc6:35","text":"PxrHairColor"}
{"item_id":"df94771dc6:36","text":"PxrHSL"}
{"item_id":"df94771dc6:37","text":"PxrInvert"}
{"item_id":"df94771dc6:38","text":"PxrLayeredBlend"}
{"item_id":"df94771dc6:39","text":"PxrMix"}
{"item_id":"df94771dc6:40","text":"PxrProjectionStack"}
{"item_id":"df94771dc6:41","text":"PxrRamp"}
{"item_id":"df94771dc6:42","text":"PxrRemap"}
{"item_id":"df94771dc6:43","text":"PxrThinFilm"}
{"item_id":"df94771dc6:44","text":"PxrThreshold"}
{"item_id":"df94771dc6:45","text":"PxrVary"}
{"item_id":"df94771dc6:46","text":"Bump（凹凸）"}
{"item_id":"df94771dc6:47","text":"创建低幅度 embossing effects（浮雕效果）。"}
{"item_id":"df94771dc6:48","text":"PxrBump"}
{"item_id":"df94771dc6:49","text":"PxrBumpMixer"}
{"item_id":"df94771dc6:50","text":"PxrNormalMap"}
{"item_id":"df94771dc6:51","text":"PxrFlakes"}
{"item_id":"df94771dc6:52","text":"aaOceanPrmanShader"}
{"item_id":"df94771dc6:53","text":"Geometry Nodes（几何节点）"}
{"item_id":"df94771dc6:54","text":"你可以使用这些节点计算 geometric properties（几何属性）和 vectors（向量）。"}
{"item_id":"df94771dc6:55","text":"PxrDirt"}
{"item_id":"df94771dc6:56","text":"PxrDispScalarLayer"}
{"item_id":"df94771dc6:57","text":"PxrDispTransform"}
{"item_id":"df94771dc6:58","text":"PxrDispVectorLayer"}
{"item_id":"df94771dc6:59","text":"PxrDot"}
{"item_id":"df94771dc6:60","text":"PxrCross"}
{"item_id":"df94771dc6:61","text":"PxrFacingRatio"}
{"item_id":"df94771dc6:62","text":"PxrTangentField"}
{"item_id":"df94771dc6:63","text":"Script（脚本）"}
{"item_id":"df94771dc6:64","text":"OSL Patterns（OSL 图案节点）"}
{"item_id":"df94771dc6:65","text":"Utility（实用工具）"}
{"item_id":"df94771dc6:66","text":"PxrAttribute"}
{"item_id":"df94771dc6:67","text":"PxrMatteID"}
{"item_id":"df94771dc6:68","text":"PxrPrimvar"}
{"item_id":"df94771dc6:69","text":"PxrVariable"}
{"item_id":"df94771dc6:70","text":"PxrToFloat"}
{"item_id":"df94771dc6:71","text":"PxrToFloat3"}
{"item_id":"df94771dc6:72","text":"PxrTee"}
{"item_id":"df94771dc6:73","text":"PxrShadedSide"}
{"item_id":"df94771dc6:74","text":"Baking（烘焙）"}
{"item_id":"df94771dc6:75","text":"这些 passthrough patterns（直通图案节点）旨在让用户能够 bake（烘焙）任意 pattern networks（图案网络）。"}
{"item_id":"df94771dc6:76","text":"PxrBakeTexture"}
{"item_id":"df94771dc6:77","text":"PxrBakePointCloud"}
{"item_id":"df94771dc6:78","text":"Guidance for Writing Your Own Patterns（编写自定义图案节点的指南）"}
{"item_id":"df94771dc6:79","text":"你不必局限于 RenderMan 提供的 patterns（图案节点）。如果遵循"}
{"item_id":"df94771dc6:80","text":"OSL Patterns（OSL 图案节点）"}
{"item_id":"df94771dc6:81","text":"中的指南，就可以构建自己的 patterns。XPU 只运行 OSL patterns，而 RIS 同时运行 C++ 和 OSL patterns。"}
